casebody.data:
May E. MCCLOUD and Vera L. Jones, in Propria Persona
v.
The FIRST JUDICIAL DISTRICT OF PENNSYLVANIA, OFFICE OF JUDICIAL RECORDS FOR FILING (AGENTS AND AGENCIES) Petition of: Vera L. Jones No. 141 EM 2017 Supreme Court of Pennsylvania. January 29, 2018

ORDER

PER CURIAM

AND NOW, this 29th day of January, 2018, the "Application for Relief for Mandate and Injunction" is DENIED.

Justice Donohue concurs in the result.
